oggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sms1665702756004.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sms1665702756004.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sms1665702756004.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sms1665702756004\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      data-uniface-role\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Custom attribute that is applied to an element in the HTML layout of a Dynamic Server Page component to bind it to a definition in the Mobile App Layout framework.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"sms1665702756004__topic_d101312e1_d101313e1_d101314e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sms1665702756004__p_d101315e1_d101316e1_d101317e1\">data-uniface-role\n                                 <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"header\"</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"content\"</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"footer\"</code> |</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"sms1665702756004__section_w5386ab1b5b3_w5387ab1b5_w5388ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sms1665702756004__p_d101318e1_d101319e1_d101320e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;div data-uniface-role=\"header\" id=\"ufld:HEADER.NME.NM\"&gt;DspContainer&lt;/div&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"sms1665702756004__section_w5389ab1b5b5_w5390ab1b5_w5391ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"sms1665702756004__table_d11915e1_d11916e1_d11917e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sms1665702756004__table_d11915e1_d11916e1_d11917e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sms1665702756004__table_d11915e1_d11916e1_d11917e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sms1665702756004__table_d11915e1_d11916e1_d11917e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">header</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sms1665702756004__table_d11915e1_d11916e1_d11917e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Identifies an element to be displayed at the top of the mobile app and that always remains visible.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sms1665702756004__table_d11915e1_d11916e1_d11917e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">content</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sms1665702756004__table_d11915e1_d11916e1_d11917e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Identifies an element to be displayed in the central application\n                           viewport. Its content may be scrolled.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sms1665702756004__table_d11915e1_d11916e1_d11917e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">footer</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sms1665702756004__table_d11915e1_d11916e1_d11917e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Identifies an element to be displayed at the bottom of the mobile app and that always remains visible.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sms1665702756004__section_czd_zdp_5wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d510809e166\">Usage</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sms1665702756004__p_d101324e1_d101325e1_d101326e1\">Use in Dynamic Server Page components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sms1665702756004__section_j2x_zdp_5wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d510809e175\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sms1665702756004__p_d101330e1_d101331e1_d101332e1\">Elements bound to the mobile app layout must be\n            direct child elements of the <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;body&gt;</code> HTML element. Otherwise the\n            element is added to the Content in the generated DSP.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sms1665702756004__p_d101333e1_d101334e1_d101335e1\">It is possible to define multiple HTML elements\n            with the same type of data-uniface-role value. For example, you can have multiple Header\n            elements or multiple Footer elements. In the generated HTML page, elements of the same\n            type are grouped together and displayed at the appropriate locations in the layout.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"sms1665702756004__fig_d101336e1_d101337e1_d101338e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>DSP for Basic Model App</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"DSP for Basic Model App\" class=\"image\" id=\"sms1665702756004__image_bmy_22p_5wb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/basicmobiledspstyleddetail.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wun1665702755914.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Mobile App Layout</a><p>Each mobile platform has its own user interface and interaction conventions, which affect the layout of a mobile application. The Mobile App Layout is a framework that maps HTML elements in a DSP layout to generic layout definitions.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615903\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615903\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "data-uniface-role Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 data-uniface-role Custom attribute that is applied to an element in the HTML layout of a Dynamic Server Page component to bind it to a definition in the Mobile App Layout framework. data-uniface-role = \"header\" | \"content\" | \"footer\" | Example: <div data-uniface-role=\"header\" id=\"ufld:HEADER.NME.NM\">DspContainer</div> Value Description header Identifies an element to be displayed at the top of the mobile app and that always remains visible. content Identifies an element to be displayed in the central application viewport. Its content may be scrolled. footer Identifies an element to be displayed at the bottom of the mobile app and that always remains visible. Usage Use in Dynamic Server Page components. Description Elements bound to the mobile app layout must be direct child elements of the <body> HTML element. Otherwise the element is added to the Content in the generated DSP. It is possible to define multiple HTML elements with the same type of data-uniface-role value. For example, you can have multiple Header elements or multiple Footer elements. In the generated HTML page, elements of the same type are grouped together and displayed at the appropriate locations in the layout. Figure 1. DSP for Basic Model App Related Links Mobile App Layout Each mobile platform has its own user interface and interaction conventions, which affect the layout of a mobile application. The Mobile App Layout is a framework that maps HTML elements in a DSP layout to generic layout definitions. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}